OL,10,G1900FAlfred Hitchcock Presents
OL,11,     GA Bullet For Baldwin: When a
OL,12,     Gworker is fired from his job, he
OL,13,     Gshoots his boss, but when he
OL,14,     Greturns to the office his boss is
OL,15,     Galive, and has no recollection of
OL,16,     Gthe incident.
